General.Name: Cascadia Investments Inc
General.Description: Cascadia Investments, Inc. operates as a real estate development company in the United States. It focuses on acquiring and renovating under-valued properties for lease and resale, as well as purchasing undeveloped real estate for the purpose of residential development and sale. Cascadia Investments, Inc. was formerly known as Freshstart Properties, Inc. The company was incorporated in 2003 and is based in Tacoma, Washington.
